{"tid":1804074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元旦遊行 偽造海報籲「全城裝修」; 警方要求「民陣」澄清, 否則「民陣」或涉煽動裝修","createTime":"2019-12-30T16:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T17:38:49.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"526d723ee56bf95a5c66987ce73854af326c5f93","tid":1804074,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A6%AA%E4%B8%AD%E9%99%A3%E7%87%9F%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E7%B1%B2-%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2599%25A3%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259F%258E%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2589%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=599277e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2599%25A3%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259F%258E%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2589%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%2F&h=bd99cdac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A6%AA%E4%B8%AD%E9%99%A3%E7%87%9F%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E7%B1%B2-%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦遊行】親中陣營瘋傳偽造海報籲「全城裝修」 警要求民陣澄清 否則或涉煽動<br />\n2019/12/30 &mdash; 14:28<br />\n<br />\n民陣將於元旦發起大遊行，主題是「毋忘承諾 並肩同行」。不過近日網上流傳一張偽造的遊行海報，將遊行主題改成「全城裝修」。民陣今日稱收到警方通知，要求他們在記者會上澄清，否則或會被視作煽動相關犯罪行為。<br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳該張海報，上面有「民陣元旦大遊行」的字眼，而海報色調及設計都與民陣相似。不過海報上「勾手指尾」的圖案設計，就被改成「舉中指」，遊行主題則被改成「毋忘報仇 全城裝修」。<br />\n<br />\n這張偽造的海報來源不明，但就在一些網上建制群組流傳。一向積極為建制陣營發聲的導演李力持亦有在FB上載這張偽造的海報，並借此批評民陣的遊行：「講明報仇預告裝修，好驚，真係好驚。」<br />\n<br />\n民陣副召集人陳皓桓今日在記者會上表示，今早收到警方的通知，指有人在網上製作海報，上面寫有「毋忘報仇 全城裝修」的標語。警方要求民陣就海報作澄清，否則或會有法律後果。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓強調該海報並非由民陣發出，但指警方應該主動調查及拘捕違法人士，而非要求民陣澄清。他呼籲警方不要恐嚇示威者及遊行發起人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>陳皓桓亦向傳媒發出該段警方的錄音短訊，警方在錄音中表明：「到時如果真的有人裝修任何舖頭時，你們（民陣）又不澄清，有機會是煽動他們的嫌疑。」</strong>"},{"pid":"0905a72edad54f99dfd6260aa277371dcd011a84","tid":1804074,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8817970579fb3217b50a00a99177431c5e34e84","tid":1804074,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"526d723ee56bf95a5c66987ce73854af326c5f93","tid":1804074,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A6%AA%E4%B8%AD%E9%99%A3%E7%87%9F%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E7%B1%B2-%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%